{"tid":1752262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"收拾心情 抗爭繼續 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T01:23:52.000Z","uid":134033,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1910b48f8b558cb1122279ef29a076ff549a77a2","tid":1752262,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:31:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要做到既係經濟攬炒<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記呢個最終目標<br />\n<br />\n不論係一年 五年定十年<br />\n<br />\n我地都要堅持落去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武抗爭一定係戰勝唔到呢個政權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果黎明行動以月做單位<br />\n<br />\n我就唔撚柒信唔經濟爆炸</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屋企呢半年輸左就快半個億  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇犧牲就唔會有收獲  而呢場運動入面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係要付出大量犧牲先會收獲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每一<span style=\"color: gold;\">票</span>都係用<span style=\"color: maroon;\">血汗淚</span>換番來</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">已經冇得退 冇得懶 冇得休息<br />\n<br />\n犧牲左太多太多人事物</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地可以得到既 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有勝利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">改善行動 並非停止行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位充滿智慧勇氣既手足 請收拾心情 繼續努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地冇得輸  諗都唔準諗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n約好左煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"320ad1089e54ddc2a15ed3a81cf0d60e748f0c24","tid":1752262,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fb828c2e4a07853f36514acb5cb7c3d4a5471a","tid":1752262,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"各位早d休息 抗爭繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71db2ee84c7b67bf811f33f34c35dd63fa353ba","tid":1752262,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:33:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8472653145a4fb732c72c9c6bf20a4c1b010b3c1","tid":1752262,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe31e46eb3e58a63ca9aba9e76c36cf00e37f3","tid":1752262,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:34:29.000Z","msg":"黎d post要推"},{"pid":"3720653ea7db434d328c8ce5c9351989a11e1c2b","tid":1752262,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57fe31e46eb3e58a63ca9aba9e76c36cf00e37f3","tid":1752262,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:34:29.000Z","msg":"黎d post要推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:35:25.000Z","msg":"手足加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc4fe35079896729d4f7721e6bb3afe50